import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import logo from "../../images/logo2.png" import burrito from "../../images/burrito.jpg" import pancake from "../../images/pancake.jpg" import egg from "../../images/egg.jpg" import spoons from "../../images/spoons.jpg" import cake from "../../images/cake.jpg" import table from "../../images/table.jpg" import veg from "../../images/veg.jpg" class WelcomeComponent extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props) this.handleSuccessfulResponse = this.handleSuccessfulResponse.bind(this) this.handleError = this.handleError.bind(this) this.state = { welcomeMessage: '', errorMessage: '' } } handleError(error) { console.log(error.response) let errorMessage = ''; if (errorMessage) { errorMessage += error.message } if (error.response && error.response.data) { errorMessage += error.response.data.message } this.setState({ errorMessage: errorMessage }) } handleSuccessfulResponse(response) { this.setState({ welcomeMessage: response.data.message }) } render() { return ( <>




Welcome to Basil!

{/* errors */}

) } } export default WelcomeComponent
